        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Member A', 3: 'This spiel... Boss is definitely going to say \"but\" again.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The team members whisper among themselves in hushed tones. You sit by the campfire, only half paying attention to the patrol captain\\'s report.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lucia is in the camp, uploading today\\'s routine data for Pyroath. Having spent so much time with her recently, being apart even for a short while feels strange for you.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Captain', 3: 'But, we\\'ve run into a new development. After speaking with the scavengers today, they told us they were unwilling to leave because they found an abandoned resort.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Captain', 3: 'They\\'ve set up quite a few sound devices over there to keep wild beasts at bay. I just went out with some of our members to check the place, and it turns out a bunch of Corrupted has already shown up...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Member A', 3: '...Good thing those guys were still worried about their two fields of crops and hadn\\'t moved into that area yet...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Captain', 3: 'Ahem! Anyway, here\\'s the plan for tomorrow: we\\'re heading to that abandoned forest resort to clear out the remaining sound devices. There\\'s a good chance we\\'ll run into more Corrupted, so stay on your guard...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Member A', 3: 'Oh great. Time for another long lecture about safety protocols and combat discipline, huh?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Captain', 3: 'Let me go over our safety protocols and combat rules one more time! Don\\'t assume you can just rush in the way Gray Raven does. Make sure you\\'re properly protected at all times...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '...', 3: '17', 4: 'He really is a conscientious captain.', 5: '17'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Member A', 3: 'He\\'s always been like this, haha—we\\'re all used to it.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He quickly picks up on your mood and gestures toward his terminal.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Patrol Member A', 3: 'Still, he\\'s a good captain. I bet... he\\'ll keep droning on for another 15 minutes.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
